  <h1 class="page-header" id="radio">Radio <a href="{{ site.repo }}/blob/{{ site.current_version }}/js/radio.js"><small>radio.js</small></a></h1>

  <p>The radio control provides a customized look and feel that can be standardized across all browsers.</p>
